B.Tx=new A.aU("This app is a web application developed using Flutter and Firebase, and requires Wi-Fi to be fully functional.\n\nFor the best user experience, view this app in portrait mode.\n\nIn the event of bugs, refresh or log out. For feedback on the app, please approach the developer directly.\n\nThere are 4 user modes:\n- Admin\n- Moderator\n- User\n- Pending Approval\n\nUsers have access to faults and vehicles screen. Only the admin and moderators can approve / suspend users, make announcements and export data.\n\n",null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
